Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.34,0:00:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在无限的时间里一切都停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.84,0:00:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类孤独的燃烧着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.14,0:00:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都没有注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.84,0:00:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界偏离了轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.30,0:00:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被红世的火焰包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在与被称作[悼词咏唱者]的弗来姆黑兹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.54,0:01:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激烈的战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.97,0:01:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜得到了新的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.70,0:02:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗 然后分离
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那时的我根本没有想到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜的新的战斗又即将开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再追逐[银]了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.53,0:02:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那是追逐也没有意义的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.22,0:02:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要再给我一些锻炼的时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.23,0:02:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你提出要锻炼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.07,0:02:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是这样...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.78,0:02:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定是偶然的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.16,0:02:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 一定是误会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:45.01,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,315}恋爱和欲望的泳池边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.86,0:02:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热啊 真是热死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.68,0:02:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么早上就这么热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:02:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天当然热了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.12,0:02:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.25,0:03:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你太懒惰了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上的锻炼虽然每天都在进行可就是没有进步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说啊 人生下来都有不同的才能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在找借口了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才到现在这个阶段说那样的话就是在逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说才能要进步一些以后再说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我啊  夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.17,0:03:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 小池
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.04,0:03:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 小池
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小池 在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.63,0:03:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我爸爸工作的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.61,0:03:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿到了很多「御崎waterland」的招待券
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经分给了班里的同学们了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「御崎waterland」是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近才开张的那个[A~HA~~]的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.28,0:04:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了夏天想到的就是泳装就是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.15,0:04:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「御崎waterland」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[A~~HA~~]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.84,0:04:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我想大家会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是非常高兴啊  真不愧是小池啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有平井同学的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你泳装怎么办 今天去买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是这种懒惰的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说夏娜 好不容易拿到了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.53,0:04:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天要不后天...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.73,0:04:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.04,0:04:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么..上课之前就对老师有意见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.76,0:04:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领带歪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:04:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是戴在中间了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.06,0:05:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二那家伙看到这一张纸就高兴成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太懒惰了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.61,0:05:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是游乐园的门票吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.89,0:05:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类不知道是什么原因好像很喜欢玩水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样想他的表现就可以理解了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.91,0:05:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里和表情都太离谱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.99,0:05:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为那样才不能进步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.22,0:05:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 阿拉斯托尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,waterland是像洗澡一样的舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.29,0:05:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.69,0:05:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去楼顶吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:06:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜 虽说在吃午饭之前也有时不回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.33,0:06:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到哪里去了啊 平井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.18,0:06:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪里了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔壁街道的面包店
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.20,0:06:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么去哪里了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.89,0:06:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 去对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.59,0:06:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜瓜面包最重要的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.22,0:06:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种脆脆的软软的口感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.46,0:06:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.40,0:06:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.66,0:06:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是方便的话大家一起吃午饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔的这样也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.84,0:07:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起边吃边聊不是觉得更加好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.52,0:07:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什什..么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的午饭一直都是便利店买的饭团啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.21,0:07:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩子要是3顿饭都吃妈妈做的饭的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.64,0:07:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不会有出息什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.24,0:07:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说要邀请悠二去waterland吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事想和大家商量一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得小池的好意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期天大家一起去waterland怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方同学..大家是指..我们大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.90,0:08:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全班同学就太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就这里的我们几个再加上他们两个怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以啊 坂井也没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.22,0:08:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班级的英雄不去可不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.80,0:08:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多好啊 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行倒是行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.67,0:08:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就这样决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:09:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期天的10点在那里集合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经决定了 不要迟到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.62,0:09:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们总是爱迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.06,0:09:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别自做主张
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方同学 不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有很多事情啊  下次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像辜负了绪方同学一片好心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.83,0:09:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期天说无论如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.31,0:09:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把玛乔丽•铎带到外面去的可是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.79,0:09:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  虽然不知道发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.42,0:09:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那天开始大姐就一直在房间里喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是再不带她四处玩玩的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要弄坏身体的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.02,0:09:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是一如既往的醉得不成样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:09:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的邪恶得沉睡公主玛乔丽•铎哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.43,0:10:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来的真是快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.30,0:10:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下又要...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.28,0:10:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样 这件泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 不用太过惹眼 这样的正好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方同学..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和男孩子一起去泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.22,0:10:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿那样朴素的泳衣怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.29,0:10:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你试穿那个之前 衣服先放在我这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.23,0:10:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是爱情 爱情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.25,0:10:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 穿上 穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.33,0:10:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.04,0:11:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那快点让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方同学 别这样了拉....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.45,0:11:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个试这个 还是这个更好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.92,0:11:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通的连衣裙式就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜 给你买了泳衣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.52,0:11:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起去游泳池啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿学校的泳装不太协调啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.11,0:11:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太协调是..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.27,0:11:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说这是穿在学校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.13,0:11:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能穿的可爱得泳衣的机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快穿上试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里等着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.31,0:11:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道不知道回避吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是误会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近处就有这样的地方夏天真是方便了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.62,0:12:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中和左藤还是来不了了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话也不接
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.91,0:12:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正他们来不来也无所谓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.47,0:12:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们5人玩的开心就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.97,0:12:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水中情侣骑马战
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.23,0:12:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男女组合进行水中骑马战
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优胜队伍的奖品是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.94,0:12:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以看到夜景的餐厅的免费用餐券
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和随意吃自制面包
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.04,0:13:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随意吃自制面包
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.87,0:13:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以看到夜景的餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为你的眼睛干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干 干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是5点才开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要参加啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.14,0:13:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参加
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想试试
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.77,0:13:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就这样决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像少了一位男士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.89,0:13:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个还是一会再想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.53,0:13:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.12,0:13:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田她们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.47,0:13:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要急 不要急
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.04,0:13:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紫和一美的泳衣秀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.25,0:13:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是平井  请~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是吉田 请~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一美..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.98,0:14:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方 我还是..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.61,0:14:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样 快来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.11,0:14:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热 要死人了 地狱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.17,0:14:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐不要这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不偶尔的外出溜溜的话身体会生病的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.65,0:14:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样看是出来对身体更不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是这样  不过..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.31,0:14:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣太 那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.94,0:14:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛乔丽小姐真的现在就要进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了啊 这种炎热的天气游泳不是正好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:15:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天吧 今天来不太适合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.87,0:15:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[悼词咏唱者]来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悼词..难道是那个人来这里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.34,0:15:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然感觉不到杀气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.99,0:15:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.97,0:15:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到两个弗来姆黑兹都来这里悠闲的玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.28,0:15:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得有点怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样 夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦人...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.26,0:15:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去买点东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.09,0:15:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.59,0:15:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊  大姐要是决定了说什么都不听啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.32,0:15:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一遇到绪方他们的话要怎么说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 这里这么多人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有那么容易就遇到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在这干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.54,0:15:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.42,0:15:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:16:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是去买点酒 荣太都在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你总是喝成那样子把他们吓到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.40,0:16:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒绝了我的邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.23,0:16:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又为什么来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.51,0:16:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想两个人来吗  到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.06,0:16:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不太清楚 好像是发生了什么争执吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.27,0:16:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是来玩玩而已吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.63,0:16:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 现在不想和你打了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.59,0:16:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是想打的话就改天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游游泳 喝喝酒 睡睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.35,0:16:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[悼词咏唱者]就满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[悼词咏唱者]作为弗来姆黑兹也结束了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.03,0:16:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过对于我们也无所谓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.11,0:17:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那昨天说不来是为了给大家一个惊喜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.37,0:17:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想要是简单的答应来的话就没什么意思了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.79,0:17:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 左藤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.62,0:17:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想在这里突然见到的话会更加热闹的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.07,0:17:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 田中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.41,0:17:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不告诉我一声
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.13,0:17:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.89,0:17:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那骑马战会参加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.49,0:17:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑马战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好 抽中同一根线的人就一队
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.04,0:17:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的人就为大家加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 大姐还等着我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.22,0:17:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办也不好办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总比说出玛乔丽的事要好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.65,0:17:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就放手了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.84,0:18:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「御崎waterland」特有的水中情侣骑马战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.46,0:18:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,规则很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抢夺到最多的头绳的队伍就是优胜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.31,0:18:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小池到底跑到哪去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.94,0:18:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说要给我们加油的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在规定时间内得到最多的头绳的情侣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.55,0:18:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以得到能够看到夜景的餐厅的免费券
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和豪华的奖品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.15,0:18:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和坂井一起到可以看到夜景的餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和坂井一起到可以看到夜景的餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.06,0:18:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了的话就可以随意吃甜瓜面包了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢了的话就可以随意吃甜瓜面包了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.87,0:18:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吧 田中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关键是你的运动力了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.74,0:18:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.88,0:18:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同学 加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.34,0:18:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用这么紧张 放松点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.82,0:18:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激烈火热的水中骑马战马上就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:18:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,限制时间是3分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.98,0:19:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起等也赢不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去攻击其他人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.36,0:19:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.90,0:19:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,归我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.66,0:19:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一美也挺能干的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.90,0:19:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.21,0:19:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑马战还是要动脑的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.84,0:19:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不动脑也没事啊  我们还有强人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.03,0:19:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样 还来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.98,0:19:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井真是了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说左藤了不起才是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不用勉强打了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.04,0:19:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.79,0:20:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的时间就还有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的情侣也不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.71,0:20:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田  好不容易才能剩下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.42,0:20:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样等待时间到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不能优胜不过还是有些奖品的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.76,0:20:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.11,0:20:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够这样呆在坂井的身边就己经很好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.50,0:20:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊  吉田
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.19,0:20:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.94,0:20:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井队又动了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.09,0:20:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.30,0:20:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要逃了  吉田
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.23,0:20:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.16,0:20:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.30,0:20:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.97,0:20:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要追过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.33,0:20:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒我们也没有意义啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦人.....
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.71,0:20:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是锻炼的一部分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.34,0:20:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太乱七八糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.80,0:20:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是乱七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能那样争吵也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田 再趴下一点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.81,0:21:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再快点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的简单
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.81,0:21:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.19,0:21:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要等
